      <bioghist id="aspace_4840d9bf562f389ae17b78803673af33">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Archives 300 was a five-year, University-sponsored project which enabled the Yale University Archives to carry out and extend its mission to document, preserve, and support research on Yale history, accomplishments, and contributions.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_cc2677b22014b3738cd200a3cae9c723">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of administrative files and the Yale Archives 300 project web site [computer files] documenting the project initiatives, staff, and history.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
